title: FIFA.World.Cup.2014.Draw.HDTV.x264-W4F.mp4
description:
FIFA.World.Cup.2014.Draw.HDTV.x264-W4F

 Gary Lineker presents live coverage of the draw from the Costa do     
 Sauipe Resort in Bahia, Brazil, as the nations discover who they      
 will face in the group stage of next summer's football tournament. A  
 total of 32 teams will take part in the competition, with the eight   
 seeded sides allocated into different groups and then drawn           
 alongside the remaining countries, with a maximum of two teams from   
 the UEFA zone in any one group.
